== INSTALL

=== Prerequisites

* <<Ruby>> 1.8.7 or newer.

* <<RubyGems>> 1.3.6 or newer.

* <<wmii>> 3.9 or newer.

=== Installing

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem install rumai
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Upgrading

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem update rumai
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Removing

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem uninstall rumai
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
